---
import experiences from "../collections/experiences.json";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative z-20 w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-16 px-7 xl:px-0 md:mt-24 lg:mt-28">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-16">

      <!-- Left: text -->
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400">
          About Me
        </p>
        <h1 class="mb-5 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight dark:text-white lg:text-5xl">
          Hi, I'm Amy Young.
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          I'm a product manager and AI builder living in Seattle. I love turning messy, complex problems into clear, useful products. And lately, I've been obsessed with what AI can do to accelerate that.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          My work sits at the crossroads of data, design, and communication. I care about building things that are not only functional but actually make sense to the people using them.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/amyyoung-data-ai/"
            target="_blank"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full bg-neutral-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-700 dark:hover:bg-neutral-200 transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 0 1-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 1 1 2.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a
            href="mailto:amy@amyyoung.me"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
            </svg>
            Send me an email
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: photo -->
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-72 h-80 md:w-80 md:h-[400px]">
        <img
          src="/assets/images/amy-young-dt.jpeg"
          alt="Amy Young"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top rounded-3xl border-8 border-white dark:border-neutral-800 shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Stats bar -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-px mt-16 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800">
      {[
        { value: "10+", label: "Years in Product" },
        { value: "30+", label: "Products Shipped" },
        { value: "5+", label: "AI Projects Built" },
        { value: "Seattle", label: "Based In" },
      ].map(stat => (
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 px-6 py-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">{stat.value}</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-medium text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-wider">{stat.label}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="w-full h-px border-t border-dashed border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 mt-20 mb-20"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- My Skills Carousel -->
  <section class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
      <div>
        <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400">Expertise</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold dark:text-white">My Skills</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <button id="skills-prev" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors duration-200">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <button id="skills-next" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors duration-200">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="skills-carousel" class="flex gap-5 overflow-x-auto scroll-smooth pb-4" style="scrollbar-width:none;-ms-overflow-style:none;">
      {[
        {
          icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09z" /></svg>`,
          title: "AI Agents & Automation",
          desc: "Building intelligent workflows, AI agents, and automation systems that save time and scale output.",
        },
        {
          icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zm9.75-9.75c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v16.5c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V3.375zm-9.75 6c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v10.5c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875V9.375z" /></svg>`,
          title: "Data & Analytics",
          desc: "Statistical analysis, business intelligence, and data visualization using R, SQL, Tableau, and Power BI.",
        },
        {
          icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h12M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-12m0 0v3.75m0-3.75h12m-6 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z" /></svg>`,
          title: "Product Management",
          desc: "End-to-end program and product development — from strategy and research to launch and iteration.",
        },
        {
          icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 15.803a7.5 7.5 0 0010.607 10.607z" /></svg>`,
          title: "Research & Strategy",
          desc: "Quantitative and qualitative research design, market analysis, UX/UI, and strategic planning.",
        },
        {
          icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.129.166 2.27.293 3.423.379.35.026.67.21.865.501L12 21l2.755-4.133a1.14 1.14 0 01.865-.501 48.172 48.172 0 003.423-.379c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0012 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018z" /></svg>`,
          title: "Communications",
          desc: "Technical and marketing communications — translating complex ideas into clear, compelling narratives.",
        },
        {
          icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5.25 14.25h13.5m-13.5 0a3 3 0 01-3-3m3 3a3 3 0 100 6h13.5a3 3 0 100-6m-16.5-3a3 3 0 013-3h13.5a3 3 0 013 3m-19.5 0a4.5 4.5 0 01.9-2.7L5.737 5.1a3.375 3.375 0 012.7-1.35h7.126c1.062 0 2.062.5 2.7 1.35l2.587 3.45a4.5 4.5 0 01.9 2.7m0 0a3 3 0 01-3 3m0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0-6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm-3 6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0-6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" /></svg>`,
          title: "Technical Infrastructure",
          desc: "Cloud platforms, Docker containerization, VPS administration, and web development.",
        },
      ].map(item => (
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-64 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
          <div class="mb-4 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-violet-50 dark:bg-violet-950 text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400" set:html={item.icon}></div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">{item.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="w-full h-px border-t border-dashed border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 mt-20 mb-20"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- My Story -->
  <section class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-16">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-[420px] h-72 md:h-[380px] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border-8 border-white dark:border-neutral-800 shadow-md">
        <img
          src="/assets/images/amy-young-sailing-3.jpeg"
          alt="Amy Young"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400">Background</p>
        <h2 class="mb-5 text-3xl font-bold dark:text-white">My Story</h2>

        <!-- Always visible -->
        <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          There's a thread that runs through everything I do: curiosity. An almost compulsive need to understand how things work, why people do what they do, and what becomes possible when you ask the right questions.
        </p>

        <!-- Expand toggle -->
        <button
          id="story-toggle"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 hover:text-violet-700 dark:hover:text-violet-300 transition-colors duration-200 mb-4 group"
        >
          <span id="story-toggle-label">It started early</span>
          <svg id="story-arrow" class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </button>

        <!-- Expandable content -->
        <div id="story-expanded" class="hidden space-y-4">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
            It started early. My dad posed math problems on long car rides, not to test me but to teach me critical thinking: that if you understand a problem deeply enough, you'll find your way to a solution. Anything is possible. Military service reinforced it differently, trading puzzles for the kind of resilience you only build by pushing past what feels like your limit.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
            Sociology and Statistics gave me a lens I've never stopped using. People plus data, together. That combination led into market research, cross-functional leadership, and eventually product management, where I could combine analytical thinking with user empathy and strategic vision, across technology, healthcare, education, and beyond. Working across industries gave me a habit of finding unexpected connections, and an appreciation for how much context shapes the way we see problems.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
            My work at the National Alzheimer's Coordinating Center brought it all into focus. Supporting the Alzheimer's research community showed me what's at stake when the right people, data, and tools find each other, and what it costs when they don't.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
            Now, with AI, the work I used to coordinate teams to do, research, design, build, and ship, I'm increasingly doing myself. I spend a lot of time exploring what's possible: building apps, agents, and automated workflows, designing systems that actually work for the people using them. It rewards exactly the kind of curious, cross-disciplinary thinking I've been practicing my whole life.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
            What an extraordinary time to be building.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    const toggle = document.getElementById("story-toggle");
    const expanded = document.getElementById("story-expanded");
    const arrow = document.getElementById("story-arrow");
    const label = document.getElementById("story-toggle-label");
    let open = false;
    toggle?.addEventListener("click", () => {
      open = !open;
      expanded?.classList.toggle("hidden", !open);
      arrow?.classList.toggle("rotate-180", open);
      if (label) label.textContent = open ? "Read less" : "It started early";
    });
  </script>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="w-full h-px border-t border-dashed border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 mt-20 mb-20"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- My Career -->
  <section class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-16">
      <!-- Left label -->
      <div class="md:w-44 flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="mb-3 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 14.15v4.25c0 1.094-.787 2.036-1.872 2.18-2.087.277-4.216.42-6.378.42s-4.291-.143-6.378-.42c-1.085-.144-1.872-1.086-1.872-2.18v-4.25m16.5 0a2.18 2.18 0 00.75-1.661V8.706c0-1.081-.768-2.015-1.837-2.175a48.114 48.114 0 00-3.413-.387m4.5 8.006c-.194.165-.42.295-.673.38A23.978 23.978 0 0112 15.75c-2.648 0-5.195-.429-7.577-1.22a2.016 2.016 0 01-.673-.38m0 0A2.18 2.18 0 013 12.489V8.706c0-1.081.768-2.015 1.837-2.175a48.111 48.111 0 013.413-.387m7.5 0V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0013.5 3h-3a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v.894m7.5 0a48.667 48.667 0 00-7.5 0M12 12.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white mb-2">Resume</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">15+ years across data, research, product, and AI.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Right: entries -->
      <div class="flex-1 divide-y divide-neutral-100 dark:divide-neutral-800">
        {experiences.map(exp => (
          <div class="py-7 first:pt-0">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-3">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class={`w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0 ${exp.avatarColor}`}>
                  {exp.shortName}
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">{exp.company}</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">{exp.role}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500 shrink-0 pt-1">{exp.dates}</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed pl-14">{exp.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="w-full h-px border-t border-dashed border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 mt-20 mb-20"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Education -->
  <section class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-16">
      <!-- Left label -->
      <div class="md:w-44 flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="mb-3 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.436 60.436 0 00-.491 6.347A48.627 48.627 0 0112 20.904a48.627 48.627 0 018.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 00-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.57 50.57 0 00-2.658-.813A59.905 59.905 0 0112 3.493a59.902 59.902 0 0110.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.697 50.697 0 0112 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 017.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0112 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 006.75 15.75v-1.5" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white mb-2">Education</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Grounded in data, people, and systems thinking.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Right: entries -->
      <div class="flex-1 divide-y divide-neutral-100 dark:divide-neutral-800">
        {[
          {
            degree: "Master of Science in Information Management",
            focus: "Data Analytics & Business Intelligence, Program & Product Management",
            school: "University of Washington",
            dates: "2022 — 2024",
          },
          {
            degree: "Bachelor of Arts, Sociology & Statistics",
            focus: "Quantitative methods, social research, and behavioral analysis",
            school: "University of Minnesota",
            dates: "1987 — 1991",
          },
        ].map(edu => (
          <div class="py-7 first:pt-0">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">{edu.degree}</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">{edu.school}</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500 mt-1">{edu.focus}</p>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500 shrink-0 pt-1">{edu.dates}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <div class="w-full h-px border-t border-dashed border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 mt-20 mb-20"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- What I Do Outside of Work -->
  <section class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-7 xl:px-0">
    <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400">Beyond Work </p>
    <h2 class="mb-3 text-3xl font-bold dark:text-white">The people and things that keep me grounded</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 text-base text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Outside of work, my family and friends are everything, and the people around my table are my anchor and my joy.</p>

    <!-- Tag pills -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
      {[
        { id: "water",     label: "Sailor & Water Sports" },
        { id: "golf",      label: "Golfer" },
        { id: "travel",    label: "Traveler" },
        { id: "food",      label: "Foodie" },
        { id: "community", label: "Community Builder" },
      ].map(tag => (
        <button
          data-beyond={tag.id}
          class="beyond-tag px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 hover:border-violet-400 hover:text-violet-600 dark:hover:border-violet-500 dark:hover:text-violet-400 transition-all duration-200"
        >
          {tag.label}
        </button>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Expandable content panels -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-0">
      <div id="beyond-water" class="beyond-panel hidden">
        <p class="py-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 border-t border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800">
          On the water is where I think best. We own a sailboat on Puget Sound, and some of my best ideas have come from somewhere on or near open water. I also paddleboard, kayak, and recently added wakeboarding to the list. Jury's still out on that one. When the seasons turn, we head to the mountains for skiing and snowboarding. The Pacific Northwest makes it easy to love the outdoors.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div id="beyond-golf" class="beyond-panel hidden">
        <p class="py-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 border-t border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800">
          I grew up playing tennis, but my friends introduced me to pickleball and now I understand why it's taken over. And then there's golf, a lifelong love affair. At its heart, golf is about nuance and complexity. It rewards patience and precision, and humbles you more often than not. But there's something about when everything clicks and it all comes together for that one amazing shot. Enough said.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div id="beyond-travel" class="beyond-panel hidden">
        <p class="py-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 border-t border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800">
          I love to travel. The anticipation of a new destination, the planning, and then the moment you set it all aside and just wander. Some of my favorite memories have come from turning down an unmarked street or saying yes to something unplanned. The unexpected delight is the point. Sharing all of it, the discoveries, the meals, the stories, with the people I love is what makes it matter.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div id="beyond-food" class="beyond-panel hidden">
        <p class="py-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 border-t border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800">
          I love to cook, but really it's about the gathering. Food is just the excuse to bring people together, mark the moments, and celebrate what matters.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div id="beyond-community" class="beyond-panel hidden">
        <p class="py-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 border-t border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800">
          My mother instilled in me early that being part of a community means contributing to it. That belief has shaped most of my adult life. I currently serve on the board of the Delridge Neighborhood Development Association, a community-based organization in Seattle that provides affordable housing and free arts, sports, and nature programming for young people. It keeps the rest of the work in perspective.
        </p>
      </div>
